data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this well maintained residence, ideally situated close to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Boasting a desirable layout, this home features a spacious primary suite and bath. There are three additional bedrooms, one of which is conveniently located in the finished basement.  The heart of this home is its open and inviting living room, adorned with tray ceilings and hardwood flooring. The kitchen has granite countertops and durable LVP flooring that extends into the cozy nook area, making it perfect for morning breakfasts. Additional features include a vast storage space behind the garage and a versatile bonus/media downstairs. Home is ideally situated just steps away from a vibrant swim and tennis facility! Enjoy the convenience and luxury of having these fantastic amenities right across the street. The private backyard, has a huge deck for hosting your next gathering or to simply enjoy the evenings. The backyard is fully fenced, offering a safe haven for play and relaxation.  This property is not just a house; it's a home waiting for new memories to be made. Don't miss the opportunity to own this gem located in a sought-after neighborhood. Schedule your visit today and experience the warmth and beauty this home has to offer!
